   "source": [
    "### <font color='#BFD72F' size=6>3.1.2 Similarity between restaurant categories</font> <a class=\"anchor\" id=\"P3.1.2\"></a>\n",
    "  \n",
    "[Back to TOC](#toc)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
